snippet.title: WARRIORS OROCHI 3 HYPER (WII U) LAUNCH TRAILER
snippet.description:
"Like" us on Facebook: http://facebook.com/koeigames
Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/tecmokoeieurope

Warriors Orochi 3 Hyper combines the much loved heroes of the Dynasty Warriors and Samurai Warriors series in a story that also features characters from Ninja Gaiden, Warriors: Legends of Troy, Bladestorm, Trinity: Souls of Zill O'll, Dead or Alive and a new character made specifically for Warriors Orochi 3 Hyper! Coming November 30 on Nintendo Wii U.
